Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To thwart Zakenja Nezo's ambitions \Nof assuming full control over Nannosho Elementary,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru bravely stood up \Nto face him and his dreadful deadly fist. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after he had been hit by Nezo's Tranquilizing Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to all his previous special trainings, Honmaru managed to mount a fierce counterattack with the power of ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, only Harako and Taruruto \Nfelt this distinctly ominous premonition so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:02:02.08,Sign,,0,0,100,,{\fade(400,0)\c&HC5D8CE&\bord0\blur0.6}Episode 59 \N{\fs50}Honmaru's Final Battle! {本丸、最後の闘い!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, I've no choice but to use the Evil Blade Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put all my power into it \Nand send out a Genuine Evil Blade Wave! {真}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's unexpected counterattack \Nseems to have put Zakenja in a predicament. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, his countenance is now more like that of a demon!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Zakenja about to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's accumulating ki at a tremendous rate! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, all of his ki is evil ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja plunged his heart into darkness \Nand is accumulating bad power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, I've only been using a fraction \Nof the Evil Blade Wave power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! This next shot will send you straight to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:04.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H01121C&\blur1\3c&H6FB6B5&\frz7.4\pos(116.54,284.36)}Fight, Edojo Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:04.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&H01121C&\blur1\3c&H6FB6B5&\frz353.2\pos(561.95,301.09)}Do your best, Class 5-1!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.55,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting too dangerous to watch, friends! \NKeep your heads down, friends! {/protect your eyes and ears/伏せる}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You might die otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but this technique, Nezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to kill Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Honmaru getting stronger and primed up \Nas he circulates that ki thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure he is! No way he'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Before our eyes, here it appears \Nout of Zakenja's back... a devilish monstruosity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he drawing the ki from Zakenja's evil heart?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! You don't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This match really is too dangerous \Nto go on any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can withstand this blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon Invocation: \NGenuine Evil Blade Wave! {降魔}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strong attack to take on! \NYet Honmaru stands completely still!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have nothin' to worry, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru will get out of this without a scratch, you'll see! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't try to oppose Zakenja's ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's absorbing it in his body instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaze Kumagoro's... Fist of Cause and Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's heart was quick to embrace \Nthe great value of Fist of Cause and Effect!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's no good, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If Zakenja-sama's attack doesn't stop soon, \Nhe won't be able to start a counter-attack!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When Honmaru accumulates enough of Zakenja's power, \Nhe'll shoot it back all at once!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Honmaru’s heart is strong enough for that?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's face is becoming like that of Zakenja's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep absorbing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorb it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorb my hatred in full!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. As the malice \Nin my pitch-black hatred stains your ki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your own ki will overwhelm your heart \Nwith my unbearable anger and sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja's heart entered my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,People are quick to betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown-ups are selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Others are indifferent to you. {/cold}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you can rely on is strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're strong, anything goes your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be someone else's slave anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make others my slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste it deep in your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The agony of my 11-year-long life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the sorrow of being betrayed by a grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Agonizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you too will live in anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soft and sweet heart, \Nnurtured by your warm and comfortable upbringing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to be dyed forever \Nwith the red-hot anger of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only time you've ever opened up your heart to another person.  {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about how strong you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're just lonely all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I be the only one to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorb that jealousy, those grudges, those grievances... \Nand fill your heart to the brim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the heart of hatred burn hot in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember all of it, \Nall of you belittling me behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All you ever do is inflict even more pain upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, it's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way you really hate us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja's conviction, and the intensity of his evil ki, are second to none!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's blood-curdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Had my soul been hit directly with this woeful malice, \Nit would have been... I would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate this world and all there is in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll follow my steps, \Nand go down the path of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you, everyone! Get lost! {g, could be he's still kind and says "take cover, everyone"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Honmaru... Friends... I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)}Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,300)}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Honmaru, I know you're not that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Honmaru, I beg you! \NI know this is within your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Come to your senses, Honmaru! {/open your eyes}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru must've absorbed \Ntons of ki of hatred that I released at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And still, the evil ki disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you willing to go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru regained his memory!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He even erased the evil ki from Zakenja's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Time for a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru returned Nezo's soiled feelings back to clean! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja is sent flying outside the arena! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Honmaru's win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Class 5-1 of Nannosho Elementary wins! {still no clue what's this tokai}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You won, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well fought, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a majestic match, Honmaru-kun.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With your own hands, you cleansed Nezo's soul. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps! Fetch a doctor at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, here's Power Upple Juice, try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is around me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what the path of fulfillment is all about? {/to be content; to have enough; to be happy; to be sufficient; to be satisfied}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck you're saying? You overcame so many trials already, \Nenough of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Route of fulfillment... What was it again? {https://twitter.com/Kintariyo/status/1488050067793719298}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, drink juice now! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Path of fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fulfillment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \NWake up! Wake up, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! Gramps will be here \Non a helicopter with a doctor in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll exhaust every option at Harako Conglomerate's disposal \Nto make sure that your sorry ass doesn't die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we gotta at least try doing CPR! {/first aid}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Give him a mouth-to-mouth artificial respiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, bring him back to life with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Me can't do that kind of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to call Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll breathe life into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ria here, he'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria - Great Great Great Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With that much "Great"-ness, she can't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! He's saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is Breathing-Into-Liferog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In emergencies, you can inhale this frog's breath, \Nthen breath life into someone you want revived. {no place for "emergency medicine" in this translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Quack, quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the introduction. \NThanks a quack and stuff. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, as beautiful and stunning as ever, quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, even I am powerless here, quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister's magic powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru died!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna give up just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Ria to kiss me! Sorry, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, please let me take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do artificial respiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm quite alive and well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am alive, can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Honmaru came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! You seen that? I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru ethereal! {幽体}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what it's all about ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't be a problem for me \Nto return to my usual body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruto! The heck you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. Keep it quiet, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru just died!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you romping about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I'm dead, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying brats. \NYou still argue even at times like this. {no clue what he means, could be "you brats seem to be in trouble", assumed he refers to jabao arguing with taru}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, Zakenja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru died because of {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru, follow me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I caused his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you were the ones who watched him die. {/let die without helping}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If he surrendered, I wouldn't have gone this far. {could be "if you surrendered"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is remembered by how you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did Honmaru win the battle against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he even tried to save his enemy's heart. {, mine}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He died as a true victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Except I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He defeated me and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for letting grade schoolers go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have stopped them no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Don't blame yourself for that, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not like you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not to blame for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You did attempt to stop the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to let them fight. It was me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed you as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to build your character as a strong man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I forgot you were still a grade schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained you harshly, \NI made you go through hardships...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reward you got out of it... \Nwas naught but this...! {unsure, could be me}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even dad is crying because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean dad loves me, after all? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You were my only true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My face is more mature than anyone else's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite my outstanding intellect, \Nmy extraordinary reflexes, my athletic body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as my enormous wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No one there could understand how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one to stand up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were different,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako and Honmaru friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Harako is the World Junior Dramatic Crying Champion too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you die in some petty brawl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You had got to be a total cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A blithering fool! {https://www.weblio.jp/content/%E3%81%8F%E3%82%8B%E3%81%8F%E3%82%8B%E3%81%B1%E3%83%BC}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa! I won't have you say whatever you want\N just 'cause I died! {hope}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here and can hear everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this to me?!{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only now realized \Nhow madly in love I was with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you have to make me feel so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Even Neyo is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't dad, it wasn't mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I loved the most in this world... \Nwas Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was selfish... I'm so sorry for all what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you were still so infinitely kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had been more honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I mustn't let Iyona-chan get that sorrowful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta return to my normal body soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, cry no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't return...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna return into my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Honmaru! Thread on your head is broken! {/cut}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An invisible thread that connects \Nthe physical body and the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens when that thread breaks, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If it broke, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you gotta return me into my body ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I can let Iyona-chan get any sadder, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Come on, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really as dead as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suck me away! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help, Taru! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru has departed for the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never believe you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... What's taking Gramps so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Open your eyes, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna part with Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! I'll totally bring you back! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sure feels good up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I even asked my mama \Nto return Honmaru home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, just you wait for me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:22:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely make it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:22:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:06.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 60 \NMagical World {まじかるワールド}
